Written for NodeMCU and tested on generic ESP8266 chips. Running against a [custom NodeMCU build](https://nodemcu-build.com) (modules: cron, crypto, enduser_setup, file, gpio, http, net, node, rtctime, sjson, tmr, uart, and wifi).

Flashing care of the wonderful [modemcu-tool](https://www.npmjs.com/package/nodemcu-tool) npm module and [esptool](https://github.com/espressif/esptool).